quran[93]{c,v,t}:
  27,1,"Taa Siin, Й—en ko Aayeeje Alqur'aanaare nden e Deftere Й“anngunde"
  27,2,Ko nde Peewal e welo-welo wonannde gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en
  27,3,"ЖҒen Й“e no ГұiiЙ“a e Julde nden Й“e totta Jakka on, hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e yananaa fii Laakara on"
  27,4,"Pellet, Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inaali Laakara on, Men cuЙ—anii Й“e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e yinoo"
  27,5,"Ko Й“en woni Й“en, Й“e woodani Й—um Lepte bonЙ—e Й—en, kamЙ“e ka Laakara ko kamЙ“e woni hayruЙ“e Й“en"
  27,6,"E pellet, an hiЙ—a lonnginee Alqur'aanaare nden immorde ka Г‘eeГұo AnnduЙ—o"
  27,7,"Tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo Й“eynguure makko nden: \"Min dey, mi haynike yiite, aray mi addana on ka nge woni Й—on kumpital maaЙ—um mi addana on docotal huЙ“Й“ungal, bela jo'o onon on iwloto"
  27,8,"Tuma nde o arunoo e magge, o noddaa: ЖҠum woni barkinaama on wonЙ—o ka yiite e Й“en wonuЙ“e banЕӢe magge, e Senayee wonanii Alla Jooma winndere nden"
  27,9,"Ko an yo Muusaa, ko woni, ko Min woni Alla TedduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o On"
  27,10,"LiЙ“u tuggordu maaЙ—a ndun, Tuma nde o yi'unoo ndu hindu dilla, a wi'ayma kayru ko ndu mboddi, o hucciti ko o doguЙ—o o yiltitaake. Ko an yo Muusaa: \"Wata a hulu, Min dey NulaaЙ“e Й“en hulataa ka Am"
  27,11,"Si wanaa on tooГұuЙ—o, refti o lontini ko moЖҙЖҙi Й“aawo bone Й—en. Pellet, Min ko Mi Surroowo YurmeteeЙ—o"
  27,12,"Naadu junngo maaЙ—a ngon ka jiiba maaЙ—a, ngo yaltay ko ngo ranewo ko aldaa e bone, [Й—um no jeyaa] e nder Aayeeje jeenay nulaaЙ—e e Fir'awna e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e laatike yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e"
  27,13,"Tuma nde arunoo e maЙ“Й“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en ko yi'eteeЙ—e, Й“e wi'i: \"ЖҠu'um, ko mbilewu Й“anngungu"
  27,14,"ЖҒe yeddi [Aayeeje Й—en], tawi wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in no yananaa fii majje, tooГұe e mawnintinaare. Ndaaru ko honno laatornoo battane fennuЙ“e Й“en"
  27,15,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Daawuuda e Sulaymaana Ganndal Й“e maaki: \"Yettoore nden woodanii Alla On Й“urnuЙ—o men e dow Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e immorde e jeyaaЙ“e Makko gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en"
  27,16,"Sulaymaana roni Daawuuda, O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, men anndinaama haala colli Й—in, men okkaama immorde e kala huunde, Pellet, Й—umЙ—oo ko Й—um woni Й“ural Й“anngungal"
  27,17,"Sulaymaana mooЙ“anaa koneeli makko Й—in immorde ka jinnaaji e ka yimЙ“e e ka colli, kamЙ“e ko Й“e yuЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e"
  27,18,"Haa nde Й“e arunoo e aynde korndolli Й—in, korndolil wi'i: \"Ko onon yo korndolli, naatee ka koЙ—anЙ—i mooЙ—on, fii wata Sulaymaana e koneeli mu'un Й—in muncu on, hara kamЙ“e Й“e so'aa"
  27,19,"[Sulaymaana] moosi ko o jaluЙ—o immorde e konngol maggi ngol, o maaki: \"Jooma, lonnginam no mi yettira neema maaЙ—a mo neeminЙ—aa e dow am on, e jibibinЙ“e lam Й“en, e nde mi gollata ko moЖҙЖҙi weltoraa Й—um, naadaami ka Yurmeende MaaЙ—a wonndude e jeyaaЙ“e MaaЙ—a moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  27,20,"O Жҙewtii colli Й—in, o maaki: \"Ko heЙ“i lam, mi yi'aali Hud-huda. Kaa ndu laati jeyaandu e wirniiЙ—i Й—in"
  27,21,"Maa mi lepta ndu sanne lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e maaЙ—um maa mi hirsandu sanne, maaЙ—um ndu addana lam hujja Й“annguЙ—o"
  27,22,"Ndu ГұiiЙ“e ko woЙ—Й—aa, ndu wi'i: \"Mi huЙ“indike ko a huЙ“indaaki Й—um, mi addanii ma immorde to Saba'i kumpital yananaangal"
  27,23,"Min dey, mi tawii sonnaajo no laamii Й“e himo okkaa immorde e kala huunde, no woodami mo kadi jullere [laamu] mawnde"
  27,24,"Mi tawii mo kanko e yimЙ“e makko Й“en hiЙ“e sujjana naange ngen gaanin Alla; Seytaane no cuЙ—aniЙ“e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en o faddii Й“e gaayi Laawol ngol, kamЙ“e Й“e feewataa"
  27,25,Ko haЙ—ata Й“e sujjana Alla On yaltinoowo ko suuЙ—ii kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi hiMo Anndi ko suuЙ—oton e ko feГұinton
  27,26,"Alla, ReweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Kanko Jooma Arsi Tedduki kin. @Corrected"
  27,27,"O maaki: \"Aray men ndaara si a goongu, maaЙ—um si laati jeyaaЙ—o e fenuЙ“e Й“en"
  27,28,"Yahidu e nduu talkuru am werloЙ—aa ndu ka maЙ“Й“e, refti huccaa Й“e ndaaraa ko honЙ—um Й“e ruttata"
  27,29,"[Sonnaajo on] wi'i: \"Ko onon yo mbatu, min dey werlaama ka am talkuru teddundu"
  27,30,"Pellet, nduu ko immorde e Sulaymaana, pellet, ko woni e mayru ko: \"Innde Alla HuuЙ“uЙ—o Yurmeende HeeriiЙ—o Yurmeende On"
  27,31,"Wata on townitano lam, aree e am ko jebbiliiЙ“e"
  27,32,"O wi'i: \"Ko onon yo mbatu, waЙ—tee lam e feere e Й—ee fiyaake am, mi laataaki taЖҙoowo fiyaake haa tawdeЙ—on e am"
  27,33,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Enen ko en jooma doole e jooma hare saЙ—tuЙ—e, fiyaake Й—en ko ka maaЙ—a woni, ndaaru ko honЙ—um yamirtaa"
  27,34,"[Debbo on] wi'i: \"Pellet, lamЙ“e Й“en si Й“e naatii e saare Й“e bonnay nde, Й“e waЙ—a tedduЙ“e mayre Й“en hoyЙ“e, ko wanonii Й“e gollirta"
  27,35,"Awa min, mi nulay e maЙ“Й“e neldaari, mi ndaara ko honЙ—um nulaaЙ“e Й“en ruttodata"
  27,36,"Tuma nde Й“e arunoo ka Sulaymaana, o maaki: \"Enee, on Й“eydiray lam jawdi, kon ko Alla okkin mi, no Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude diini kon ko O okki on, ko woni, onon hiЙ—on farnora neldaari mooЙ—on ndin"
  27,37,"Rutto ka maЙ“Й“e, mamen addana Й“e koneeli Й—i Й“e maraa feere muuЙ—um, mamen yaltin Й“e ton ko Й“e jaasuЙ“e hara kamЙ“e ko hoyЙ“e"
  27,38,"O maaki: \"Ko onon yo mbatu, ko hommbo e mooЙ—on addanta lam jullere laamu makko nden, ko adii Й“e arude ka am ko Й“e jebbiliiЙ“e"
  27,39,"Ngaari jinna ndin wi'i: \"Min, mi addante nde ko adii a immaade e darnde maaЙ—a nden, e pellet, min e dow Й—um ko mi dolnuЙ—o hoolaaЙ—o"
  27,40,"On mo woni ka muuЙ—um ganndal immorde ka Deftere wi'i: \"Min mi anndante nde ko adii a nde ndarЙ—e maaЙ—a Й—en ruttotoo e maaЙ—a\". Tuma nde o yi'unoo nde ko nde ГұiiЙ“unde ka makko, o maaki: \"ЖҠum Й—oo, ko immorde e ЖҒural Joomi am, fii yo O ndarndo lam si mi jarnay [Mo] maaЙ—um si mi yedday [Mo], kala jarnuЙ—o anndu ko o jarni kon wonanay wonkii makko kin, kala yedduЙ—o kadi pellet, Joomi am ko O Galo TedduЙ—o"
  27,41,"O maaki: \"Faytinanee mo jullere laamu makko nden, ndaaren si on annditay, kaa o laatoto jeyaaЙ—o e Й“en Й“e annditataa"
  27,42,"Tuma nde o arunoo, [o] wi'aa: \"Enee, ko nii jullere maaЙ—a nden wa'i?\" O wi'i: \"Awi'ayma ko kayre tigi nii\". Men okkaama ganndal ko adii mo, men laatii jebbiliiЙ“e"
  27,43,"Faddii mo, Й—um ko o laatinoo himo rewa gaanin Alla, pellet, kanko o laatinoke jeyaaЙ—o e yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e"
  27,44,"Wi'anaa mo: \"Naatu ka huЙ“eere\". Tuma nde o yi'unoo nde o sikki ko nde duneere(tewru), o Гұori dense (korle)makko Й—en. [Sulaymaana] maaki: \"Pellet, ndee ko huЙ“eere newЙ—iniraande ndaarorЙ—e\". [Debbo on] wi'i: \"Jooma, min dey mi tooГұii wonkii am, mi jebbilanike Alla Jooma winndire nden, wonndude e Sulaymaana"
  27,45,"GomЙ—ii Men Nulii faade e SamuudinkooЙ“e Й“en musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Saalihu, Й—um woni rewee Alla. Tawi kamЙ“e ko Й“e feddeeji Й—iЙ—i hiЙ“e wennjondira"
  27,46,"O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, ko fii honЙ—un heГұornton bone Й—en ko adii moЖҙЖҙere nden?\" \"Ko haЙ—i insinanino Alla bela jo'o onon on yurminoyte"
  27,47,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men kiitinorii ma e Й“en wonnduЙ“e e maaЙ—a\". O maaki: \"kiite mooЙ—on on ko ka Alla woni, ko woni, onon ko on yimЙ“e fitneteeЙ“e\" @Corrected"
  27,48,Laatinoke ka saare ton worЙ“e njeenayo hiЙ“e bonna ka leydi Й“e moЖҙЖҙintaa
  27,49,"ЖҒe wi'i: ЖҒe woondirii Alla, ma men waalanan mo ka suudu kanko e Й“eynguure makko nden refti ma men wi'an jeyЙ“e mo Й“en; men tawaaka warugol yimЙ“e makko Й“en, e pellet, menen ko men goonguЙ“e\". @Corrected"
  27,50,"ЖҒe hodi hodoore Menen kadi Men fewji fewjoore, tawi kamЙ“e Й“e so'ataa"
  27,51,"Ndaaru, ko honno laatorno battane hodo maЙ“Й“e ngon, Menen Men yirbinno Й“e kamЙ“e e yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e"
  27,52,"ЖҠin cuuЙ—i maЙ“Й“e ko yeewuЙ—i sabu ko Й“e tooГұunoo kon. Pellet, wonii e Й—um Maande wonannde yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e Й“en"
  27,53,"Men danndi Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e woni hulooЙ“e [Alla]"
  27,54,"E Luutu, tuma nde o wi'anno yimЙ“e makko Й“en: 'Enee, on aray pankare Й—en hara hiЙ—on sutii"
  27,55,"Eyoo, onon on aray e worЙ“e Й“en ka tuuyo accon rewЙ“e Й“en?! Si ko woni, onon ko on yimЙ“e majjaaЙ“e"
  27,56,"Jaabawol yimЙ“e makko Й“en wonaano si wanaa ko Й“e wi'i : \"Yaltinee yimЙ“e Luutu Й“en ka hoЙ—o (wura) mooЙ—on ; kamЙ“e ko Й“e yimЙ“e laЙ“Й“intintooЙ“e"
  27,57,"Men daЙ—ndi mo kanko e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, si wanaa debbo makko on; [on Й—on] Men hoddiranii mo ko o jeyaaЙ—o e halketaaЙ“e Й“en"
  27,58,"Men toЙ“ini e dow maЙ“Й“e toЙ“o, bonii toЙ“o jertinaaЙ“e Й“en"
  27,59,"Maaku: Yettoore nden ko Alla woodani, kisiyee wonii e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en Й“e O suЙ“ii. Enee, ko Alla Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, kaa ko Й—in Й—iЙ“e sirkanta"
  27,60,"Kaa ko hommbo tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin O jippinani on immorde ka kammu ndiyam? Men fuЙ—iniri Й—am gese joomiraaje ЕӢari. Wonantaa on nde fuЙ—inon leЙ—Й—e majje. Enee, hara reweteeЙ—o no woodi wonndude e Alla? Ko woni, kamЙ“e ko Й“e yimЙ“e ooГұotooЙ“e"
  27,61,"Kaa ko hommbo waЙ—i leydi ndin ГұiiЙ“undi, O waЙ—i hakkunde mayri calluЙ—i O waЙ—ani ndi pelle O waЙ—i hakkunde maaje Й—en Й—iЙ—i heedo? Enee, hara na woodi reweteeЙ—o [goo] wonndude e Alla? ko woni, Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude Й“en e maЙ“Й“e Й“e anndaa"
  27,62,Kaa ko hommbo jaabato Й“ittiiЙ—o on si o noddi Mo o hunca bone Й—en O waЙ—a on lontiiЙ“e ka leydi? Na woodi KoreweteeЙ—o goo wonndude e Alla? FanЙ—ii ko waajitoЙ—on
  27,63,"Kaa ko hommbo fewnata on ka niЙ“e njoorndi e ka maayo, e ko hommbo accitata keni Й—in wewlinirayЙ—i fii Yurmeende Makko nden? Enee, ko reweteeЙ—o goo wonndude e Alla? Alla Toowii gaayi ko Й“e sirkata kon. @Corrected"
  27,64,"Kaa ko hommbo woni fuЙ—Й—uЙ—o tagu ngun refti O rutta ngu, e ko hommbo arsikata on immorde ka kammu e ka leydi? Enee, ko reweteeЙ—o goo wonndude e Alla? Maaku: \"Addee daliili mooЙ—on on si tawii ko on goonguЙ“e"
  27,65,"Maaku: \"Anndaa ko wirnii kon Й“en wonuЙ“e ka kammuuli e ka leydi si wanaa Alla. ЖҒe so'ataa kadi ko honnde tuma Й“e immintinoytee"
  27,66,"Ko woni, ganndal maЙ“Й“e ngal hattii fii Laakara on, ko woni, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e e sikke fii [Laakara], ko woni, kamЙ“e ko Й“e wumuЙ“e fii Й—um"
  27,67,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e wi'i: \" Enee, hay si men laatike mbullaari e baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en kadi, e hara menen ko men yaltinoyteeЙ“e"
  27,68,"GomЙ—ii men fodanooma Й—um menen e baabiraaЙ“e amen ko adii, Й—um wonaali si wanaa tinndi adinooЙ“e"
  27,69,"Maaku : \"Yehee ka leydi ndaaron ko honno battane bonЙ“e Й“en laatornoo"
  27,70,"Wata a suno fii maЙ“Й“e, wata a laato e Й“itteende immorde e ko Й“e fewjata kon"
  27,71,"HiЙ“e wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  27,72,"Maaku: \"No tijjaa nde tawata Й“adanike on yoga e kon ko Й—aЙ“Й“uЙ—on yaccinaneede"
  27,73,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a ko O Jom ЖҒural e dow yimЙ“e Й“en, kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude Й“en e maЙ“Й“e Й“e jarnataa [Alla]"
  27,74,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a hiMo Anndi ko Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en soomi e ko Й—e feГұГұinta kon"
  27,75,"Alaa e wirniikun ka kammu e ka leydi si wanaa [fii makkun] no e nder Deftere Й“anngunde"
  27,76,"Pellet ndee Alqur'aanaare, hinde filloo e dow Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en fii huunde nde Й“e Й“uri luutondirde nden e fii muuЙ—um"
  27,77,"Pellet, kayre ko nde peewal e Yurmeende wonannde gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en"
  27,78,"Pellet, Joomi maaЙ—a O Гұaawiray hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Г‘aawoore Makko ngal, ko Kanko woni TedduЙ—o AnnduЙ—o"
  27,79,"Wakkilo e Alla, pellet, an hiЙ—a e hoore Goonga Й“annguka kan"
  27,80,"Pellet, an a nanintaa mayЙ“e Й“en, a nanintaa faaЙ—uЙ“e Й“en noddaandu ndun si Й“e Й—uurnike Й“e huccitii"
  27,81,An a wonaali fewnoowo bumЙ“e Й“en e gaayi majjere maЙ“Й“e nden. A nanintaa si wanaa Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e jebbiliiЙ“e
  27,82,"Si konngol ngol yanii e dow maЙ“Й“e, Men yaltinana Й“e daabewa immorde ka leydi himba haalana Й“e wonnde yimЙ“e Й“en laatike Й“e yananaaka Aayeeje Amen Й—en"
  27,83,E Гұalnde Men mooЙ“oyta immorde e kala mofte dental jeyaaЙ“e e Й“en fennooЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e soggee
  27,84,"Haa si Й“e arii, O Daala: \"Eyoo, on fenniino Aayeeje Am Й—en, hara on huЙ“indoraali Й—i ganndal. Kaa ko honЙ—um wonЙ—on e gollude"
  27,85,"Konngol [Lepte] ngol yani e maЙ“Й“e sabu ko Й“e tooГұi kon, kamЙ“e Й“e wowlataa"
  27,86,"Enee, hara Й“e yi'aali, Menen Men waЙ—ii jemma on fii yo Й“e deeЖҙu e maako, e Гұalorma on yi'irЙ—o? Pellet, wonii e Й—um Aayeeje wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e Й“en"
  27,87,"E Г‘alnde wuttoytee ka alaadu, Й—enЖҙoo Й“en wonuЙ“e ka kammuuli e Й“en wonuЙ“e ka leydi, si wanaa Й“en Й“e Alla muuyi, gooto kala e maЙ“Й“e aray e Makko hara ko Й“e hoykiniiЙ“e"
  27,88,"HiЙ—a tina pelle Й—en, sikka ko Й—e fenndiiЙ—e, hara le kannje hiЙ—e wuloo wulagol duule Й—en, Й—um ko kuugal Alla, On ЕӢarЙ—inЙ—o kala huunde, pellet, Kanko ko O HumpitiiЙ—o ko golloton kon"
  27,89,"Mo ardii e moЖҙЖҙere nden haray no woodani mo ko Й“uri nde moЖҙЖҙude, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e hooliiЙ“e immorde e Й—enЖҙere nden Г‘alnde"
  27,90,"Mo ardii kadi e bone Й—en, geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en hippete ka Yiite. Yalli on yoЙ“ete si wanaa kon ko laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on golla"
  27,91,"Anndu ko mi yamiraa ko yo mi Rewu Jooma ndii leydi ndi Alla harmini Й—um, no woodani Mo kala huunde. Mi yamiraama kadi yo mi laato jeyaaЙ—o e jebbiliiЙ“e Й“en"
  27,92,"E yo mi janngu Alqur'aanaare nden, mo feewii haray ko hoore-makko o feewani, mo majjii kadi haray maaku: \"Min dey, ko mi jeyaaЙ—o e jertinooЙ“e Й“en"
  27,93,"Maaku kadi: \"Yettoore nden woodanii Alla, aray O holla on Aayeeje Makko Й—en anndon Й—e\". Joomi maaЙ—a wonaali welsindiiЙ—o gaay e kon ko golloton"